## ✅ what i did  
-clicked start
-opened the terminal
-ran: '/challenge/check'
-ran in a new terminal: 'rm -rf /'
-ran again with: 'rm -rf --no-preserve-root /'
-flag popped out after a while in the other terminal

## 🧑🏾‍🏫 what this challenge teaches u
command rm -rf / forcefully deletes every file and directory from the root of the system making it completely unusable

